and collective MI/EW tasks/skills by replicating the complex (simulation) operational environment and setting the conditions to
train intelligence system operators and analysts on the intelligence cycle (Planning/Direction, Collection, Processing, Analysis/
Production, Dissemination). IEWTPT development directly supports training for core intelligence tasks such as Intelligence
Support to Force Generation, Intelligence Support to Situation Understanding, Conducting Information Collection, Intelligence
Support to Targeting and Information Operations. Capabilities enable ISR (Intelligence, Surveillance, and Reconnaissance)

