       Increase of $3.083 million for AN/BPS-17 Radar Improvements.
       Increase of $0.400 million for SLD SABERR improvements.
       Decrease of $4.215 million for Contractor Support Savings.
       Decrease of $13.238 million for other programmatic, rate, and miscellaneous adjustments.

