D. Acquisition Strategy
The single, full-scale MSV(L) prototype will undergo contractor and government testing through FY 2026. Following prototype testing the prototype vessel may be used
as a test bench for future modifications and/or a training asset.

 Family of MSV: The Army will perform affordability and feasibility studies to inform acquisition strategies and requirements. Competitive design efforts will result in digital
 prototypes which will further inform acquisition strategies and requirements. Family of MSV acquisition strategies maximize competition at every phase of design,
 prototyping, and test to yield the most affordable and achievable position for the Army in the program's production phase.




