enhance Joint Interoperability through Army Cloud based capabilities across the Cross Domain Solutions (CDS). Additionally,
SIMCI will look to participate in a NATO Modeling and Simulation group to provide expertise on technical solutions/standards with
NATO partners.

3) Mission Command Support - Will continue collaboration between PEO STRI and PEO C3N following MVP events to enable
testing and integration activities.

4) SIMCI Support to Simulation and Mission Command - Architect support will remain imbedded with PEO C3N to enable
interoperability testing and certification events between legacy and developing Simulation and Mission Command capabilities.
