This effort supports the ASA(ALT) Data Steward and performs the duties as the Functional Data Manager in Army Data
Environment. Governance Forums including the Army Data Board (ADB), Army Analytics Board (AAB) and JADC2 Working
Groups. In addition to representing the ASA(ALT) in Army data forums improving the ASA(ALT) data environment through the
